{"tid":1357033,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（認真POST）大家就住星期六元朗個遊行原則有共識未？！","createTime":"2019-07-23T15:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T16:27:48.000Z","uid":16365,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cd8380743c7bf7787831f154b0a8979f7d888320","tid":1357033,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:46:32.000Z","msg":"大家耐性有限，我長話短說，因為已預計到去元朗危險性好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 我地愈和平，就顯得上星期日果班恐怖份子愈暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：</span></span><br />\n- 政府想個局面變成「暴徒」對暴徒（甚至短期目標係兩邊開拖嘅電視畫面），然後幫警察開脫，不能成全佢<br />\n- 而家民意企哂我地果面，要令市民有好深印象，我地兩班人係唔同層次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 不主動挑釁白衫，但會自衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n- 而家係去元朗表達五大訴求加反黑，唔係去撩交打<br />\n- 自衛意思係只用足夠保護自己同同伴嘅武力，唔係衝入人地村破壞，有人俾我地打走，唔好離隊追，好似之前新城市果個ON9差佬咁<br />\n- 實際考慮：黑警實由你兩邊打，我地在明，黑社會在暗，一D都唔著數，黑社會48小時後一定放走，我地唔係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3. 結伴前去，起碼4-5人一小隊</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n- 西鐵沿線都會有危險，由出門口一刻開始就要好小心，直到番到屋企為止<br />\n- 散場要快，唔好走D唔走D，走得慢果D好危險<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4. 一定要齊裝備</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n- 對手都要保護好，好多時見大家赤手空拳用對手擋，實死<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多，但仲有一個位要傾：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 去到邊個位退場？<br />\n- 到終點即散？！<br />\n- 喺西鐵站做D咩？做完先走？</span><br />\n<br />\n唔想再出現有人撤，有人唔想撤嘅情況，要走就一齊走<br />\n<br />\n如大家有共識，請推到行動當日，確保大家on the same page。請出招。"},{"pid":"523b09c9e5d2bcd041db10bf172707b0316ee595","tid":1357033,"uid":165246,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:46:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"37c6f4b437cd8af2564d6cf86d1d0b07a7b36026","tid":1357033,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:47:36.000Z","msg":"弱弱一推"},{"pid":"f7073c951de16574562ccf9ca9674611c498add8","tid":1357033,"uid":263038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:49:07.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n一定要有共識"},{"pid":"50dae6357016c74915ca0ad075f6ad20b8c0f57b","tid":1357033,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d294690e92e410aecc1656bfd5ee779da1ceea","tid":1357033,"uid":16365,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:49:11.000Z","msg":"上星期日喺中環有D叫走，有D叫唔走，最後有兄弟中彈，好傷心<br />\n希望大家可以再溝通多D"},{"pid":"a1ba1844ee730f93d02e0f1957d927261e8599f1","tid":1357033,"uid":49536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:50:30.000Z","msg":"其實發起人應該要開記者會講明呢幾點<br />\n仲要點明呢個係俾警隊證明能否有能力有信心保護市民<br />\n警隊必定要同遊行人士既安全捆綁埋一齊<br />\n少一條頭髮都要正副處長問責"},{"pid":"4415349b33a46bdb8711737bacea3223ecc695c0","tid":1357033,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:51:07.000Z","msg":"我認同：<br />\n1. 各有各做<br />\n2. 前線巴打最清楚現場情況，大家應相信其判斷<br />\n3. 唔應該輕易撤<br />\n<br />\n但希望大家，唔好聽到其他聲音就起哂鋼先<br />\n大家目標一致，<br />\n唔岩傾到岩"},{"pid":"46e68589d593104911afd0ee5820ce91e03fc630","tid":1357033,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:53:35.000Z","msg":"我最怕嘅結果係：<br />\n到時有白衫挑釁，未必數量好多，但有好一部分行行下開始離隊，前面/後面D人唔知<br />\n你追我我追你，入埋村，周圍無狗無記者，<br />\n真係出事都無人知"},{"pid":"34bae0240521d21f8031e08d8a94b5bbe779c037","tid":1357033,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1ba1844ee730f93d02e0f1957d927261e8599f1","tid":1357033,"uid":49536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:50:30.000Z","msg":"其實發起人應該要開記者會講明呢幾點<br />\n仲要點明呢個係俾警隊證明能否有能力有信心保護市民<br />\n警隊必定要同遊行人士既安全捆綁埋一齊<br />\n少一條頭髮都要正副處長問責"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:55:17.000Z","msg":"今日有位朋友做代表申請不反對通知書<br />\n我諗佢好難做呢樣野，<br />\n佢未必代表到大家，<br />\n除非呢度已有明顯共識"},{"pid":"377a6c56b8956d54278b948f61d9d1d497640056","tid":1357033,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e64c571573217b56cafd93c85537d760049e956","tid":1357033,"uid":263038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:58:13.000Z","msg":"大家記住<br />\n對抗嘅唔只係黑社會<br />\n仲要班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebb4afc130d47de3ab7f06b3286021f879d6051","tid":1357033,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:58:17.000Z","msg":"anyone"},{"pid":"0c57647cbc9ead6737a731cd93233b440875df31","tid":1357033,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e64c571573217b56cafd93c85537d760049e956","tid":1357033,"uid":263038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:58:13.000Z","msg":"大家記住<br />\n對抗嘅唔只係黑社會<br />\n仲要班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:58:51.000Z","msg":"點睇咩情況下先散得水？"},{"pid":"1a77d74788d9962a19fb1d0adaed7061451044eb","tid":1357033,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kil